  "title": "VP/SVP Cpaas Product lead",
  "description": "<p>We're seeking a strategic leader to drive growth and innovation in our clients platform-based products and new business initiatives across the Asia region </p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ol><li>Develop and execute regional product strategy for CPaaS, Telco APIs, AI-enabled solutions, and digital products</li><li>Collaborate with senior stakeholders to co-create initiatives and drive market launches</li><li>Lead product planning, roadmap development, and go-to-market strategies</li><li>Foster strategic partnerships to accelerate time-to-market</li><li>Drive regional adoption through workshops, strategy sessions, and business planning forums</li><li>Develop compelling value propositions to attract new members and partners</li><li>Pursue regional enterprise opportunities with our Member Operators</li><li>Lead a high-performing team of 4-5 members</li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Engineering, Marketing, or International Business</li><li>15+ years of experience in telecommunications</li><li>5+ years of product management experience</li><li>5+ years in leadership and people management</li><li>3-5 years working experience in Asia</li><li>Excellent communication and negotiation skills</li></ul>",
